<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Thank you for booking your flight, <%= @passenger.name %></h1>
    <p>
      You have successfully booked your flight with the airline.<br>
      Your departure airport is <%= @passenger.flight.departure_airport.code%>.<br>
      Your arrival airport is <%= @passenger.flight.arrival_airport.code%>.<br>
      The date/time is <%= @passenger.flight.departure_date %>.<br>
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for booking and have a great day!</p>
  </body>
</html>